      • getKeyName

        @NonNull
java.lang.String getKeyName​(@NonNull
                            SubType subType)
        Returns the keyName for the given SubType.

        The key name is the identifier of the authenticator (from getIdentifier(), concatenated with the string representation of the sub type.

        Parameters:
        subType - the sub type of the requested key name
        Returns:
        if sub type is not null - the name of the key
        otherwise - an empty string
